Description_lang: The vial of Black Blood shatters and spills its contents, creating a pool that inflicts $s1 Shadow damage and absorbs the next $s2 healing received every $t1 sec from players within the effect.Eggs that come in contact with the pool hatch, releasing horrific creatures that attack players.
